      additionalProperties: false

      properties:
        data:

        statusCode:

        enable:
          type: boolean
        object:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ObjectType'
      required:
        - data
        - enable
      additionalProperties: false
    ProjectApi.CreateFunc.Response:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        uuid:
          type: string
      required:

        - uuid
      additionalProperties: false
    ProjectApi.UpdateFunc.Request.Body:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string

          type: string

        - data
      additionalProperties: false

        - id
      additionalProperties: false
    ProjectApi.GetFunc.Response:
